2026-01-06 11:21:30 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1767698490,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"13.48.147.148","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/114.0.0.0 YaBrowser\/22.7.0 Yowser\/2.5 Safari\/537.36","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":11463,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"100","project_id":"834","nick":"Porter","topic":"Start 2026 the right way!","content":"Hi\r\n\r\nTired of spending money on marketing? Lets start 2026 the right way.\r\n\r\n1. Find your competitors\r\n2. Receive their clients\r\n3. Make Money\r\n\r\nWhy do this?\r\nBecause of advertising practices of major platforms like Google, Facebook, and YouTube.\r\n\r\nIt seems quite frustrating that these companies charge advertisers repeatedly for the same leads, especially when they clearly understand the market dynamics.\r\n\r\nIn contrast, we believe in transparency and fair competition. We provide our clients with access to customer data previously purchased by others, they receive details about leads that would have otherwise cost them thousands. \r\n\r\nPlus, we offer daily updates for a month, ensuring they stay informed about their competitive landscape at no extra cost. \r\n\r\nVisit us for a free sample!\r\nhttps:\/\/Porter.marketing2.cfd?domain=studioatrium.pl","create_date":"2026-01-06 11:21:30","modify_date":"2026-01-06 11:21:30","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2934575},"entity_changes":false}
